reviews.text:
Now this is a Simple and Delicious Juice!! Exactly what the creators notes say, I mean EXACTLY! &#xD;
I added WS23 and I can recommend it, goes very well with the zesty Tartness from the Lemon profile. My simple description would be a Lemon meringue Ice cream. The zest part of this almost reminds me of the tartness form a lemon Cheesecake. Loads of Flavor especially considering is a low 8.5% on total flav % from these 3 concentrates.  I vaped this as a shake and vape and enjoyed it all the way to the recommended steep date, it does improve with steep, but goes well for me as a SnV.&#xD;
Thank you and Well Done on this Zugmaschine, I enjoyed this one!!
